text: Jim O'Regan (23 April 1938 - 15 May 1998) was an Australian cricketer. He played six first-class matches for New South Wales in 1957/58. ==See also== * List of New South Wales representative cricketers ==References== ==External links== * Category:1938 births Category:1998 deaths Category:Australian cricketers Category:New South Wales cricketers Category:Cricketers from Sydney
